==English==

===Noun===
'''[[Middle]] [[Ages]]'''

#In history, the Middle Ages is the period of time between the decline of the Roman Empire and the revival of letters (the [[Renaissance]]). Hallam regards it as beginning with the sixth and ending with the fifteenth century.

